'''Courtenay Taylor''' (born [[July 19]], [[1960s#1969|1969]]) was the voice of [[Juhani]] in ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' and additional characters in ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''. Later, Taylor provided additional voices for the ''[[Star Wars Jedi]]'' [[Star Wars video games|video game]] series.<ref name="Survivor">''[[Star Wars Jedi: Survivor]]''</ref>

==''Star Wars'' voice work==
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' {{C|Juhani}}
*''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]'' {{C|Additional voices}}
*''[[Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order]]'' {{C|Additional voices}}
*''[[Star Wars Jedi: Survivor]]'' {{C|Additional voices}}

